---
title: Chicken, Coconut & Chermoula Veggie Soup with Crushed Cashew Nuts & Roasted Pumpkin
description: There’s something special about settling down after a long day with a warm aromatic soup. We’re leaning
into the comfort factor by roasting the veggies and adding them to the chermoula-spiced creamy chicken soup.
Garnish with roasted cashew nuts and you’re in for a nutritious and relaxing night.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
